Third-party data attribution
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Transcriptomic data are derived from the NASA Open Science Data Repository
(OSDR / GeneLab, https://osdr.nasa.gov) and released under the NASA Open Data
policy. Please cite the individual OSD accessions used in this meta-analysis
(see the manuscript). Orthology assignments use OrthoDB v12
(https://www.orthodb.org).
